      "id": "/page/0/Text/4",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">Basel II prescribes the use of Value-at-Risk as a risk measure for OR, with a confidence level of 99.9% and a measurement horizon of 1 year. Hence,</p>",
