      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">i stands for the number of past observation years; <math display=\"inline\">\\mathcal{B}</math>stands for the different BL, typically <math display=\"inline\">B = 8</math>; <math display=\"inline\">R</math>denotes the different risk types (RT); often <math display=\"inline\">R = 7</math>: <math display=\"inline\">N</math>(frequency) denotes the number of losses in year <math display=\"inline\">T - i</math>, BL b, and RT r; and (severities) denotes the successive loss amounts <math display=\"inline\">X</math>in these classes.</p>",
