    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/1",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">classes. We firmly believe that, before reaching this ultimate goal, we have to walk up and down the quantitative risk management hill a couple of times. The final satisfaction with the results obtained may crucially depend on this.</p>",
      "page": 230,
      "polygon": [
