      "id": "/page/1/Text/5",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\" class=\"has-continuation\">So far, we have only briefly mentioned the stochastic modeling of the internal OR loss data. The regulators require a combination of internal with external and expert opinion data. Several companies are providing industrywide OR loss data on which banks can calibrate their internal loss distribution</p>",
