      "id": "/page/1/TextInlineMath/15",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">A related mathematical problem we would like to point out at this point is the following: suppose <math display=\"inline\">X_1, \\ldots, X_d</math> are d one-period risks, <math display=\"inline\">\\Psi: \\mathbb{R}^d \\to \\mathbb{R}</math>a function corresponding to a financial position <math display=\"inline\">\\Psi(X_1,\\ldots,X_d)</math>, and <math display=\"inline\">\\rho</math> a risk measure so that we want to calculate (estimate)</p>",
